						               													<description>Night has come in London, Van Helsing, famous vampire hunter is tracking Dracula. Their final fight will take place tonight. Will Van Helsing defeat Dracula before he turns all London&amp;rsquo;s inhabitants into vampires?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player plays a different character: either Van Helsing or Dracula.&amp;#10;In order to win, Van Helsing must remove all Dracula&amp;rsquo;s life points. If Dracula turns all 4 inhabitants of the same District into vampires, Dracula player becomes the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;How to play?&amp;#10;A game is played in 5 rounds maximum. Each round, players play in turn, drawing a card and discarding a card to trigger its ability.&amp;#10;On their turn, a player draws a card from the deck. Then, they  can discard this card or swap it with any of their 5 cards, discarding the chosen card. They then triggers the ability of the discarded card. There are 8 kinds of cards with different effects. The turn is now over and the next player starts their turn.&amp;#10;Instead of drawing (and discarding) a card, a player can call the end of the round. In order to choose this action, at least 6 cards need to be in the discard pile. Opponent plays a last turn, then it&amp;rsquo;s the end of this round.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
